#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Das Chinesische Mah-Jongg-Spiel by Uwe Martens 2005, Books on Demand GmbH, "
"Norderstedt. This book is an excellent German reference containing "
"everything you want to know about the rules used in Germany and many other "
"aspects of the game."
msgstr ""
"Das Chinesische Mah-Jongg-Spiel द्वारा Uwe Martens 2005, Books on Demand "
"GmbH, Norderstedt. इदं पुस्तकं उत्तमः जर्मन-सन्दर्भः अस्ति यस्मिन् जर्मनीदेशे प्रयुक्तानां "
"नियमानाम् अन्येषां च अनेकेषां पक्षानां विषये यत् किमपि ज्ञातुम् इच्छति तत् सर्वं समाविष्टम् अस्ति "
"।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:986
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Complete Book of Mah-Jongg by A. D. Millington, 1977 (with several "
"paperback editions up to 2003), Weidenfeld &amp; Nicolson, London. This is "
"the ultimate reference for Classical Chinese Mah Jong as played in the "
"Western world. It can give you valuable hints about game strategies."
msgstr ""
"ए.डी.मिलिंगटनस्य मह-जोङ्गस्य सम्पूर्णपुस्तकं, १९७७ (२००३ पर्यन्तं अनेकपत्रपृष्ठसंस्करणैः सह), "
"Weidenfeld &amp; निकोल्सन, लण्डन्। पाश्चात्यजगति यथा क्रीड्यते तथा शास्त्रीयचीनीमाह "
"जोङ्गस्य अन्तिमः सन्दर्भः एषः अस्ति । एतत् भवन्तं क्रीडारणनीतीनां विषये बहुमूल्यं संकेतं दातुं "
"शक्नोति।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:988
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mah-Jong by Gwyn Headley and Yvonne Seeley, 3rd edition, 2008, A &amp; C "
"Black Publishers Ltd., London. This book is a very easy to use reference, "
"concentrating on the rules as used in Great Britain, defined by the BMJA "
"(The British Mah Jong Association)."
msgstr ""
"Gwyn Headley and Yvonne Seeley द्वारा मह-जोङ्ग, तृतीय संस्करण, 2008, ए &amp; सी "
"ब्लैक पब्लिशर्स लिमिटेड, लण्डन। अयं पुस्तकः अतीव सुलभः सन्दर्भः अस्ति, यत्र ग्रेट् ब्रिटेनदेशे "
"यथा प्रयुक्ताः नियमाः केन्द्रीकृताः सन्ति, ये बीएमजेए (The British Mah Jong "
"Association) इत्यनेन परिभाषिताः सन्ति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:996
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "संस्थापनम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:997
#, no-c-format
msgid "For Linux: Your distribution should have it packaged for you."
msgstr "Linux कृते: भवतः वितरणं भवतः कृते तत् संकुलितं भवितुमर्हति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1000
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For Windows: Please see <ulink url=\"https://www.linux-apps.com/p/1109453/"
"\"></ulink> for a Windows installer."
msgstr ""
"Windows कृते: कृपया Windows संस्थापकस्य कृते <ulink url=\"https://www.linux-apps.com/"
"p/1109453/\"></ulink> पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1003
#, no-c-format
msgid "If you want to download the source and install manually:"
msgstr "यदि भवान् स्रोतः डाउनलोड् कृत्वा मैन्युअल् रूपेण संस्थापनं कर्तुम् इच्छति:"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:1006
#, no-c-format
msgid "git clone https://invent.kde.org/games/kajongg.git"
msgstr "git clone https://invent.kde.org/games/kajongg.git"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1007
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For Linux: <literal>cd kajongg ; mkdir build ; cd build; cmake .. &amp;&amp; "
"make &amp;&amp; make install</literal>"
msgstr ""
"लिनक्सस्य कृते: <literal>cd kajongg ; mkdir निर्माणम् ; cd build; cmake .. &amp;"
"&amp; make &amp;&amp; संस्थापनं कुरुत</literal> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1008
#, no-c-format
msgid "For Windows: Please read <filename>README.windows</filename>"
msgstr "विण्डोज कृते: कृपया <filename>README.windows</filename> पठन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1011
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Kajongg depends on those packages: (debian package names in parentheses)"
msgstr "Kajongg तेषु संकुलानाम् उपरि निर्भरं भवति: (कोष्ठकेषु debian संकुलनामानि)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1014
#, no-c-format
msgid "Python 3.8 or higher (python3)"
msgstr "पायथन् ३.८ अथवा उच्चतरम् (python3) ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1015
#, no-c-format
msgid "Qt6.5 or higher (python3-pyqt6 and python3-pyqt6.qtsvg)"
msgstr "Qt6.5 अथवा उच्चतर (python3-pyqt6 तथा python3-pyqt6.qtsvg)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1016
#, no-c-format
msgid "the python bindings for Qt6 (python3-pyqt6)"
msgstr "Qt6 (python3-pyqt6) कृते पायथन् बन्धनानि"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1017
#, no-c-format
msgid "the python twisted library 16.6.0 or higher (python3-twisted)"
msgstr "the python twisted library 16.6.0 अथवा उच्चतरम् (python3-twisted)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1018
#, no-c-format
msgid "sqlite3 (libsqlite3-0)"
msgstr "sqlite3 (libsqlite3-0) 1.1."
